This is my current version of my dh/nazgul deck.  I knew I wanted to slim the deck down even more after i never drew elrond in those last two games against Dan.  Then I saw Farmer Maggot in Patrick&#39;s deck in the finals, and thought i would give it a shot, and he is amazing.  Using Merry every turn of a game with the Farmer and Elrond is just stupid.  Other than that, you can look at my Dragon*Con Day 2 5th place to check out my take on this deck.<br />
